---
title: Leek, Bacon & Crumbly Cheese Chicken Breast with Rosemary-Roasted Kumara
description: A few simple touches make this meal really special. Finishing the chicken with the sauteed leek and creamy Greek-style cheese allows it to soak up lots of lovely flavours, while the rosemary gives the kumara a rich, aromatic quality.
From ordinary to extraordinary in just a few simple steps!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/leek-feta-grilled-chicken-c8f723de.jpg
